milestones.description: Greenidge has broken the record for most sixes (13) in ODIs for WI, going past Viv Richards's 11
Alvin Kallicharran has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (25) for WI, going past Clive Lloyd
Greenidge has broken the record for most sixes (13) in ODIs, going past Viv Richards's 11
Jeremy Coney and Warren Lees's 54-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 27 between Vic Pollard and Bruce Taylor
